SafeOnline Performance Agent Distribution

 This artifact produces a ZIP containing a JBoss Application Service bundled with the performance agent service.
 
* Linux

 The performance agent service is using JGroups for discovery.
 
 This requires multicast to be allowed on a firewalled linux box.
 
 On Fedora this can be achieved via:
 
+---+
iptables --insert RH-Firewall-1-INPUT -d 224.0.0.0/4 -j ACCEPT
+---+